1509707-a.title: 15th Street - Second Avenue looking east
1509707-a.folder: 15th Street - Second Avenue looking east, Manhattan, NY

711322f-a.text:
224-200 East 15th Street, south side, west from, but not including Second to Third Aves., as viewed across the N.W. corner of Rutherford Place. No. 220 is the German Masonic Temple and it is under renovations.

June 30, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.
